  "synopsis": "This is a beautiful and magical legend. The cheerful and outgoing Miao girl, Na Sheng, embarks on a long journey to find her dream home—Yunhuang—to escape the chaos of the world. But is Yunhuang truly the legendary paradise? With each step she takes deeper into Yunhuang, a series of bizarre and thrilling events unfold, filled with bloodshed and adventure. A cast of distinctive and extraordinary legendary figures also appear, weaving poignant and moving mythological tales… \n\n(Source: Tencent, translated)",
